				<wikidot:authorName>Flawed</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3089916</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Pardon me, but I'm a bit confused here. What is the purpose of the embedded system? Based on the scip's name I guess it has something to do with exploring the solar system, but why minor planets and their names? Is there something from the displayed text that I'm missing? Anyways, an explanation would be great.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
